 capabilities to Small and Midsize Businesses. For more information, please
 see /usr/share/doc/ledgersmb/README.Debian.
 .
 The application now defaults to being made available on port 5762 and being
 run directly by Starman instead of by Apache. If other access is also needed,
 a Reverse Proxy can be configured locally using Nginx or Apache, and this
